  m_text: 'Game Objective:

    Survive until the time limit is up!


    How To
    Play:

    Select your character (each character comes with their own predetermined
    weapon).

    Kill enemies to gain experience.

    Level up and choose an upgrade
    (add a new weapon/passive item to your inventory or upgrade an existing one).

    Survive
    until the time is up.

    Weapons will automatically fire in intervals.


    Controls:

    WASD
    keys to move around'
